text: Lake Dahlgren is a lakeTravelOK. "Dahlgren Lake" Retrieved August 23, 2013. situated approximately southeast of Noble, Oklahoma. It is an artificial lake created by the Oklahoma Department of Wildlife Conservation in 1953. There are no picnic, camping or bathroom facilities at Lake Dahlgren. However, the lake remains popular due to the numerous hiking trails located nearby. ==Notes== Category:Bodies of water of Cleveland County, Oklahoma Dahlgren Category:Tourist attractions in Cleveland County, Oklahoma
title: Lake Dahlgren
